findings.title: Owner can change admin address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change the admin address.

findings.title: Owner can change treasury address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the treasury address.

findings.title: Admin can change pid value
findings.description: The admin has the privilege to modify the pid value.

findings.title: Admin can change performance fee value
findings.description: The admin has the privilege to modify the performance fee value.

findings.title: Admin can change call fee value
findings.description: The admin has the privilege to modify the call fee value.

findings.title: Admin can change withdraw fee value
findings.description: The admin has the privilege to modify the withdraw fee value.

findings.title: Admin can change withdraw fee period
findings.description: The admin has the privilege to modify the withdraw fee period which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Admin can call MasterChef’s emergency withdraw
findings.description: The admin has the privilege to call MasterChef's emergency withdraw function, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Admin can withdraw tokens from the contract
findings.description: The admin has the privilege to withdraw tokens from the contract without any restrictions.

findings.title: Admin can pause and unpause contract (no deposit, no harvest)
findings.description: The admin has the capability to pause and unpause the contract without any restrictions or requirements for deposits or harvesting.
